verse = \lyricmode {
  Give to the Lord of lords re -- nown;
The text \"the King of kings with glory crown.\" only contains 8 syllables, but 11 are required. There's a \"mismatch —\" the text as given cannot be split into exactly 11 syllables.
His mer -- ci -- es ev -- er shall en -- du -- re,
when lords and kings are known no more.
}
